{"name": "SUNCOAST COMMUNITY HEALTH CENTER -PLANT CITY", "alternate_name": "", "description": "* Our Social Services Specialist will assist you with the completion and filing of the following applications on Access Florida:
	* Medicaid
	* Food Stamps
	* Cash Assistance
	

* Please bring the following items to your appointment:
	* Case # (if available)
	* Check Stubs (last 4 weeks)
	* SSNs for the entire family
	* Utility bills
	* Rent/Mortgage statements
	* Daycare expenses (need address, phone and amount paid)
	
 
* We stay with you all the way!
	* Pending Medicaid approval, we help you choose your healthcare plan and/or assist with provider changes
	* We help you manage your MyAccess Account
	* We follow up on EBT (food stamps) accounts/lost cards or not received
	* Help enroll your newborn baby into Medicaid
	* Schedule appointments for the WIC Program (Be sure to bring: Proof of Income; Picture Id; SSN; Immunization
	* Record to your appointment)", "email": "", "url": "suncoast-chc.org", "status": "active", "address": {"address_1": "801 East Baker Street", "address_2": null, "city": "Plant City", "state_province": "FL", "postal_code": "33563", "country": "US"}, "location": {"latitude": 28.0180814, "longitude": -82.118271}, "phones": [{"number": "(813) 653-6100", "type": "voice"}], "regular_schedule": [{"weekday": "Monday", "opens_at": "11:30", "closes_at": "21:00"}, {"weekday": "Tuesday", "opens_at": "11:30", "closes_at": "21:00"}, {"weekday": "Wednesday", "opens_at": "11:30", "closes_at": "21:00"}, {"weekday": "Thursday", "opens_at": "11:30", "closes_at": "21:00"}, {"weekday": "Friday", "opens_at": "11:30", "closes_at": "21:00"}]}
